## 7. Completed Features

### Merge Controller System
- ✅ First merge timing bucket calculation (Immediate / AfterABit / AfterNeglect)
- ✅ Sleep metronome (drains 0.02/s during gotchi mode)
- ✅ Merge lock cooldown (3 seconds after each beat)
- ✅ Voluntary merge gating with VOLUNTARY_MERGE_UNLOCKED flag
- ✅ Forced merge when sleep hits 0
- ✅ Climax handling (deathEnabled prevents return to gotchi)

### Story Sequencer System
- ✅ 6 story beats with authored scene order
- ✅ StoryBeatStarted event triggers scene switch
- ✅ Dialog completion triggers StoryBeatCompleted
- ✅ Climax beat sets deathEnabled and emits DeathEnabled
- ✅ SLIDE_RIGHT transition for door/step-through effect

### Simulation Reducer (C-Core)
- ✅ Sleep drain while seenReality is true
- ✅ Affection driver from warmth actions (pet, groom, water)
- ✅ Mercy driver from merge events (weighted by earliness)
- ✅ Grime creep during neglect
- ✅ Collapse detection when deathEnabled and needs are critical

